name: ANTI-GOD #001
description:
We don't need them, bringing these damn "god stone" or whatever we should not rely on them.

Since they came down everything changed.

Look at our schools our university, our laboratory, they took everything, I even know one of our best searcher who left us to become a "Apostle" or whatever that means.

I will bring them down.

All of them so we can get back our world.

A world where science and intelligence is king, a world where they need ME AND MY IDEAS
